safeeval = SafeEval(load_numpy=True, load_scipy=True)
literals = ['[3, 5, 7, 9]', 'list(range(50, 1001, 50))',
    'np_arange(0.01, 1, 0.1)',
    'np_random_choice(list(range(1, 51)) + [None], size=20)',
    'scipy_stats_randint(1, 11)']
for li in literals:
    assert safeeval(li) is not None
x_safeeval = SafeEval(load_estimators=True)
literals = [
    '[sklearn_tree.DecisionTreeRegressor(), sklearn_tree.ExtraTreeRegressor()]'
    ,
    '[sklearn_feature_selection.SelectKBest(), sklearn_feature_selection.VarianceThreshold(), skrebate_ReliefF(), sklearn_preprocessing.RobustScaler()]'
    ]
for li in literals:
    assert x_safeeval(li) is not None
